reviewText: A Very nice 3 set of movies - Worth to buy.

I bought and sent it as a gift.  My friend liked the 3rd one (Sexual Roulette) for its story and atmosphere.  Of course, it is personal
feeling.  The 1st one (Loaded) is an average crime-fighting story.  The 2nd one (Lost) --- I forgot what he said, sorry.

This DVD has 3 movies.  Go for it.
Bought this for and only watched LOST. It's one of Dean Cain's better performances.
